Class RingBuffer<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • scicoms.RingBuffer<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type to be held within this data structure

    public class RingBuffer<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    Implements a dynamically typed ring buffer. Maintains a fixed number of objects. When the structure is at some pre-defined capacity, kills the oldest entry to make room for a new entry.
    Author:
    Aaron Pabst
